title: Iran claims missile barrage near US consulate in Iraq - The Associated Press - en Español
content: Iran claims missile barrage near US consulate in Iraq  The Associated Press - en EspañolView Full Coverage on Google News
description: BAGHDAD (AP) — Iran claimed responsibility Sunday for a missile barrage that struck near a sprawling U.S. consulate complex in northern Iraq, saying it was retaliation for an Israeli strike in Syria that killed two members of its Revolutionary Guard earlier this week.
